Note: Variables and Data Types

name = "Abneesh"
age = 20
salary = 50000.50
isStudent = true

Print "Name: " + name
Print "Age: " + age
Print "Salary: " + salary
Print "Is Student: " + isStudent

Note: You can also use Create for explicit types
Create integer named score equal to 95
Print "Score: " + score

Note: Reassignment
Set age to 21
Print "Updated age: " + age
